    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a factory 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a linear power delivery through its six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been fully overhauled with Beisan Systems components. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the rod bearings replaced with VAC coated shells. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by a fresh set of bushings and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, providing exceptional turn-in and lateral grip. The paint depth is consistent with factory standards, and the interior retains its original tactile quality with no bolster wear or pixel degradation in the cluster. This is a turn-key, investment-grade icon for the performance purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
